s|TAG_BIO_2011_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Amitabh Bachchan Signed For Hollywood Movie, The Great Gatsby</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan Signed For Hollywood Movie, The Great Gatsby" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2011/09_05_2011.html">09/08/2011</A>:  <br> Veteran Bollywood actor <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> will finally make a debut in Hollywood. Mr. Bachchan was signed for upcoming movie by Baz Luhrmann, titled The Great Gatsby. The movie stars Leonardo Dicaprio (famous for his role in movie Titanic) in the title role, and also includes <A ALT="" TITLE="Tobey Maguire" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/celebrites/tobey_maguire/celebrites_tobey_maguire.html">Tobey Maguire</A> (famous for his role as Spiderman), Joel Edgerton, Carey Mulligan, Isla Fisher, Jason Clarke and also features newcomer Elizabeth Debicki. The movie will start shooting this week in Sydney, Australia. Mr. Bachchan will be seen in the role of Meyer Wolfsheim. The movie is an adaptation of the F Scott Fitzgerald novel. The film has an estimated budget of $125 million and will be shot in 3D. <b>Kareena Kapoor To Be Added To Madame Tussauds Wax Museum</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Kareena Kapoor To Be Added To Madame Tussauds Wax Museum" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2011/06_13_2011.html">06/16/2011</A>: <br> Bollywood actress <A ALT="" TITLE="Kareena Kapoor" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/kareena_kapoor/bollywood_kareena_kapoor.html">Kareena Kapoor</A> will be added to the Madame Tussauds wax muserm along side other Bollywood personalities like <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Shahrukh Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/shahrukh_khan/bollywood_shahrukh_khan.html">Shahrukh Khan</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Salman Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/salman_khan/bollywood_salman_khan.html">Salman Khan</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Zindagi Milegi Na Dobara Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2010/zindagi_milegi_na_dobara.html">Zindagi Milegi Na Dobara (2010)</A> . Kareena's wax statue will be unveiled at the new Madame Tussauds museum in UK’s Blackpool September 2011. Then it will tour other museums in the US, Europe and Asia, starting with Bangkok in January 2012, followed by Hong Kong, Los Angeles, Las Vegas, Washington DC, Berlin, Amsterdam, Vienna and ending at London. Kareena, also known as Bebo, is currently busy shooting with <A ALT="" TITLE="Salman Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/salman_khan/bollywood_salman_khan.html">Salman Khan</A> for their upcoming film <A ALT="" TITLE="Bodyguard Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2011/bodyguard.html">Bodyguard (2011)</A> . Kareena is the brand ambassador of a Size Zero laptop, has a pizza and clutch purse named after her and now she will be immortalised in wax.|g
