s|TAG_BIO_2010_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Clash Of The Bollywood Titans On TV</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Clash Of The Bollywood Titans On TV" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2010/08_30_2010.html">09/02/2010</A>: <br> The new TV season will open with a clash between Bollywood titans, <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Salman Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/salman_khan/bollywood_salman_khan.html">Salman Khan</A> . Both will be hosting their TV shows the on the different networks. Mrs. Bachchan will host <A ALT="" TITLE="Kaun Banega Crorepati 4" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/tv_shows/kaun_banega_crorepati/kaun_banega_crorepati_04.html">Kaun Banega Crorepati 4</A> while Salman Khan will be hosting <A ALT="" TITLE="Bigg Boss 4" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/tv_shows/bigg_boss/bigg_boss.html">Bigg Boss 4</A> on Colours TV Channel.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Hrithik Roshan Wax Figure In Madame Tussauds London</b> <br> <font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Hrithik Roshan Wax Figure In Madame Tussauds London" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2010/07_05_2010.html">07/05/2010</A>: </font> <br> Bollywood star <A ALT="" TITLE="Hrithik Roshan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/hrithik_roshan/bollywood_hrithik_roshan.html">Hrithik Roshan</A> will join <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Salman Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/salman_khan/bollywood_salman_khan.html">Salman Khan</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> as the next Bollywood actor to have his wax figure at the famous Madame Tussauds in London. Hrithik is currently in Spain shooting for his next film, <A ALT="" TITLE="Zindagi Milegi Na Dobara Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2010/zindagi_milegi_na_dobara.html">Zindagi Milegi Na Dobara (2010)</A> .<BR> <A ALT="" TITLE="Shahrukh Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/shahrukh_khan/bollywood_shahrukh_khan.html">Shahrukh Khan</A> 's wax figure was the first one for a Bollywood star in the Madame Tussauds in Los Angeles.|g
