s|TAG_BIO_2009_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Bigg Boss 3 Contestants</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bigg Boss 3 Contestants" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/10_05_2009.html">10/05/2009</A>: <br> The list of contestants for the new season of <A ALT="" TITLE="Bigg Boss 3" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/tv_shows/bigg_boss/bigg_boss.html">Bigg Boss 3</A> on tv channel Colors have been announced. The show will be hosted by <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> . The list includes Bollywood movie actress <A ALT="" TITLE="Sherlyn Chopra" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/sherlyn_chopra/bollywood_sherlyn_chopra.html">Sherlyn Chopra</A> , Shilpa's little sister <A ALT="" TITLE="Shamita Shetty" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/shamita_shetty/bollywood_shamita_shetty.html">Shamita Shetty</A> . Aditi Gowitrikar a former Mrs World 2001, ex-Gladrags champion who also starred on first season of Khatron Ke Khiladi. Music director Ismail Darbar sho provided hit songs from Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam, Tera Jadoo Chal Gaya and <A ALT="" TITLE="Devdas Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2002/devdas.html">Devdas (2002)</A> . Jaya Sawant, mother of Rakhi Sawant. German super model, singer and actress Claudia Ciesla. Former Miss India and Bollywood actress from the the 80s Poonam Dhillon. Comedian Raju Srivastav, designer Rohit Varma, Kamaal R Khan, Vindoo Dara Singh, and the married couple Bakhtiyar and Tanaz Irani.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Amitabh Bachchan To Host Season 3 Of Bigg Boss</b> <br> <font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan To Host Season 3 Of Bigg Boss" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/09_07_2009.html">09/07/2009</A>: </font> <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> has agreed to host the season 3 of <A ALT="" TITLE="Bigg Boss 3" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/tv_shows/bigg_boss/bigg_boss.html">Bigg Boss 3</A> . Big B will be seen interacting and guiding the behaviour of the inmates of the house. The first promos of the show will be hitting the TV really soon.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Aishwarya Rai Bachchan The Most Powerful Female Actor In India</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan The Most Powerful Female Actor In India" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/04_13_2009.html">04/15/2009</A>: <br> In an recent survey by Hansa Research, Indian film actress <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai (Aishwarya Bachchan)" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> came out to be most powerful female actor in India, ahead of <A ALT="" TITLE="Priyanka Chopra" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/priyanka_chopra/bollywood_priyanka_chopra.html">Priyanka Chopra</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Katrina Kaif" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/katrina_kaif/bollywood_katrina_kaif.html">Katrina Kaif</A> and even <A ALT="" TITLE="Madhuri Dixit" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/madhuri_dixit/bollywood_madhuri_dixit.html">Madhuri Dixit</A> . Aishwarya was at par with cinematic legends like <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> and cricketing star <A ALT="" TITLE="Sachin Tendulkar" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/sports/cricket/sachin_tendulkar/cricket_sachin_tendulkar.html">Sachin Tendulkar</A> and was the only female who is part of the top 10 recognized celebrities from all walks of life. The survey also pointed out that Aishwarya is one of the most popular faces among classes as well as the masses.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Bachchanalia: The Films and Memorabilia of Amitabh Bachchan</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bachchanalia: The Films and Memorabilia of Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2009/01_05_2009.html">01/06/2009</A>: <br> A pictorial book called 'Bachchanalia: The Films and Memorabilia of Amitabh Bachchan' has been released to cover the four decade long journey of Mr. <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> . The book is written by journalist Bhawna Somaiya and been published by Osian. The book was released at Tata Theatre in the National Centre for Performing Arts (NCPA) in South Mumbai.|g
