s|TAG_BIO_2008_LATEST_NEWS|<b>Amitabh Bachchan Released From Hospital</b> <br> <font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan Released From Hospital" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/10_13_2008.html">10/17/2008</A>: </font> <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> has been discharged from <A ALT="" TITLE="Maharashtra Mumbai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/Regional/India/Maharashtra/Mumbai/Mumbai.html">Mumbai</A> 's Leelavati Hospital after being in the hospital for about a week for abdominal pains. It so happended that the day he was admitted to the hospital the superstar was celebrating his 66th birthday. He was accompanied by his son <A ALT="" TITLE="Abhishek Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/abhishek_bachchan/bollywood_abhishek_bachchan.html">Abhishek Bachchan</A> daughter in law <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> and daughter Shweta Nanda. This will bring a big relif to thousands of his fans across the country who had been praying for a speedy recovery for Mr. Bachchan. <BR> Now it seems that Aishwarya's father Krishna Raj Rai has also being admitted to the hospital. Her father had been diagnosed with cancer last year and is undergoing cancer treatment at Hinduja hospital.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Aishwarya Rai And Amitabh Bachchan To Perform At Live Earth Concert 2008</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai And Rajnikanth Shooting For Enthiram" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/09_15_2008.html">09/21/2008</A>: <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> are once again going to perform live on stage together. Last time they were part of the <A ALT="" TITLE="Unforgettable Tour 2008" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/info/bollywood_concert.html">The Unforgettable Tour</A> and now they will be dancing at the Live Earth concert to be held at the Andheri Sports Complex on December 07 2008 in <A ALT="" TITLE="Maharashtra Mumbai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/Regional/India/Maharashtra/Mumbai/Mumbai.html">Mumbai</A> , India. Jon Bon Jovi and Shekhar Kapur will also be performing on stage. The event is being organized by Al Gore, former vice president and 2007 Nobel Peace Prize, and Kevin Wall.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>Sarkar Raj Headed For Oscar Library</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Sarkar Raj Headed For Oscar Library" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/08_04_2008.html">08/06/2008</A>: <br> Ram Gopal Varma's <A ALT="" TITLE="Sarkar Raj Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2007/sarkar_2.html">Sarkar Raj (2008)</A> script is going to be added to the prestigious Academy of Motion Pictures Oscar Library. The script will at the library permanently for the students of media. The movie was about the political issues, and the power games played by the politicians against each other and starred <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Abhishek Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/abhishek_bachchan/bollywood_abhishek_bachchan.html">Abhishek Bachchan</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> in the pivtol roles. Films like <A ALT="" TITLE="Devdas Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2002/devdas.html">Devdas (2002)</A> , Kal Ho Na Ho and Lagaan have already been added to the prestigious library that were produced by the Indian Film industry.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"> <b>PETA Announcenes Asia's Sexiest Vegetarians</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="PETA Announcenes Asia's Sexiest Vegetarians" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/06_23_2008.html">06/25/2008</A>: <br> PETA, People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals, named Bollywood film star <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> was named Asia's sexiest male vegetarian while Chinese singer and actress Faye Wong was named as Asia's sexiest female vegetarian. Wong edged out Die Hard 4 beauty <A ALT="" TITLE="Maggie Q" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/celebrites/maggie_q/celebrites_maggie_q.html">Maggie Q</A> .<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>The Bachchan's 'Unforgettable' World Tour</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="The Bachchan's Unforgettable World Tour" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/05_26_2008.html">05/28/2008</A>: <br> The Bachchan's are in preparation for their world tour called <A ALT="" TITLE="Unforgettable Tour 2008" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/info/bollywood_concert.html">Unforgettable Tour</A>, . The tour is set to being on July 18, 2008 in Toronto followed by performances at Trinidad, Tobago, Houston, Atlantic City, New York, Vancouver, and London. Currently <A ALT="" TITLE="Abhishek Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/abhishek_bachchan/bollywood_abhishek_bachchan.html">Abhishek Bachchan</A>, <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A>, and <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> are rehearsing the performances at a hall in Juhu, <A ALT="" TITLE="Maharashtra Mumbai" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/Regional/India/Maharashtra/Mumbai/Mumbai.html">Mumbai</A> . Aishwarya will be performaing the hit 'Dola re..' number from <A ALT="" TITLE="Devdas Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2002/devdas.html">Devdas (2002)</A> with <A ALT="" TITLE="Madhuri Dixit" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/madhuri_dixit/bollywood_madhuri_dixit.html">Madhuri Dixit</A>, . The Bachchan family trio will also be performing the famous song 'Kajra re' from the hit movie <A ALT="" TITLE="Bunty Aur Babli Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2005/bunty_aur_babli.html">Bunty Aur Babli (2005)</A> . Others joining the tour include Bollywood actors <A ALT="" TITLE="Preity Zinta" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/preity_zinta/bollywood_preity_zinta.html">Preity Zinta</A>, , <A ALT="" TITLE="Akshay Kumar" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/akshay_kumar/bollywood_akshay_kumar.html">Akshay Kumar</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Riteish Deshmukh" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/ritesh_deshmukh/bollywood_ritesh_deshmukh.html">Riteish Deshmukh</A> , choreographer Shiamak Davar and music duo of <A ALT="" TITLE="Vishal Dadlani" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/music_director/vishal_dadlani/bollywood_vishal_dadlani_filmography.html">Vishal Dadlani</A> and <A ALT="" TITLE="Shekhar Ravjiani" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/music_director/shekhar_ravjiani/bollywood_shekhar_ravjiani_filmography.html">Shekhar Ravjiani</A> .<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Bollywood Stars At Cannes Film Festival 2008</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Bollywood Stars At Cannes Film Festival 2008" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/05_05_2008.html">05/09/2008</A>: <br> Bollywood made it's presences felt at the 2008 Cannes Film Festival being held in Cannes, France. Bollywood star <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> was present with the her new family including husband <A ALT="" TITLE="Abhishek Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/abhishek_bachchan/bollywood_abhishek_bachchan.html">Abhishek Bachchan</A>, father in law <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> and mother in law Jaya Bachchan. <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_rai/bollywood_aishwarya_rai.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> was at the Cannes as part of her role as a model for L'Oreal and was pictured with Hollywood stars <A ALT="" TITLE="Eva Longoria" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/actress/eva_longoria/hollywood_eva_longoria.html">Eva Longoria Parker</A> . Also present was <A ALT="" TITLE="Angelina Jolie" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/hollywood/actress/angelina_jolie/hollywood_angelina_jolie.html">Angelina Jolie</A> with husband Brad Pitt. Earlier in the day Angelina was seen at the premiere of her new animated film Kung Fu Panda along with costars Dustin Hoffman and Jack Black.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Aishwarya Rai Bachchan Going On World Tour</b> <br> Date: <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan Going On World Tour" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/news/2008/03_17_2008.html">03/21/2008</A>: <br> There is no vacation for <A ALT="" TITLE="Aishwarya Rai Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actress/aishwarya_bachchan/bollywood_aishwarya_bachchan.html">Aishwarya Rai Bachchan</A> this summer. She has been busy the last six months finish her movies and now she will be travling on a world tour called Unforgettables along with her husband, <A ALT="" TITLE="Abhishek Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/abhishek_bachchan/bollywood_abhishek_bachchan.html">Abhishek Bachchan</A> , and father in law, <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A>.|g
