h Bachchan</b> <br> Date: 04/05/2006 <br> Ram Gopal Verma announces another project in the mist of still finalizing his current project, <A ALT="" TITLE="Sholay Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/sholay.html">Sholay</A> . RGV announced <A ALT="" TITLE="Nishabd Movie Review" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/nishabd.html">Nishabd</A> , staring <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> and the story is about a 54-year old married man who falls in love with a girl, 36 years younger. The film is scheduled to start production May 1, 2006. The film is based on Vladimir Nakobov’s timeless novel Lolita.<br><hr size="1" width="100%"><b>Amitabh Bachchan begins shooting after surgery</b> <br> Date: 03/20/2006 <br> <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> has begun to shot for this movies after his surgery. He is currently shooting for Karan Johar's <A ALT="" TITLE="Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/kabhi_alvida_na_kehna.html">Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna</A> (Never Say Goodbye). This is the first time the actor has entered the studio since his stomach surgery in Dec 17, 2005. Also in the news is that Sony has acquired the music rights of <A ALT="" TITLE="Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/movie_reviews/2006/kabhi_alvida_na_kehna.html">Kabhi Alvida Naa Kehna</A> being directed by Karan Johar and stars <A ALT="" TITLE="Amitabh Bachchan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/amitabh_bachchan/bollywood_amitabh_bachchan.html">Amitabh Bachchan</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Shahrukh Khan" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/actor/shahrukh_khan/bollywood_shahrukh_khan.html">Shahrukh Khan</A> , <A ALT="" TITLE="Rani Mukherjee" HREF="http://www.bollywoodmovies.us/